20000505170100000_17	This rule is going to go so much further in enhancing vehicle safety it s unprecedented.	thi rule go go much enhanc vehicl safeti unpreced
20000505170100000_18	NHTSA also will require vehicles to be tested using a family of dummies an average size man a small woman and 1 3 and 6 year old children.	nhtsa also requir vehicl test use famili dummi averag size man small woman year old children
